image_analysis.description: A scanned page from a document, likely a report or briefing book, featuring a collage of eight photographs related to Jeffrey Epstein. Each photograph is accompanied by a descriptive caption. The images include personal photos of Epstein with associates, a mugshot, photos of a jail cell and correctional facility, a courthouse photo, a screenshot of a sex offender registry entry, and an aerial view of his private island.
image_analysis.layout: A multi-panel layout with images and text captions arranged in two main columns. The left column has four images and their captions, and the right column has four images and their captions. A document number is present at the bottom right corner.
